Meet Scott Jacobs. Scott Jacobs is a Middelburg resident who enjoyed his first visit to Cape Town at 73 years of age. At 73 years of age, Scott Jacobs visits Cape Town for the first time! Scott is a huge tennis fan and to treat him, his family bought him a ticket to the Match in Africa. Accompanied by a friend and fellow tennis player, Scott and Henning Benadie attended the match at the Cape Town Stadium.
